f, and is clovenfooted, and cheweth the cud, among the beasts, that shall ye eat.","year":-1490},{"id":"recW4VMYOajn6funK","ref":"Lev.11.4","text":"Nevertheless these shall ye not eat of them that chew the cud, or of them that divide the hoof: as the camel, because he cheweth the cud, but divideth not the hoof; he is unclean unto you.","year":-1490},{"id":"rec5CejFD7s3k6nri","ref":"Lev.11.5","text":"And the coney, because he cheweth the cud, but divideth not the hoof; he is unclean unto you.","year":-1490},{"id":"rec3LUDaI9L3azDtR","ref":"Lev.11.6","text":"And the hare, because he cheweth the cud, but divideth not the hoof; he is unclean unto you.","year":-1490},{"id":"recG1I3GbQuv5b3YM","ref":"Lev.11.7","text":"And the swine, though he divide the hoof, and be clovenfooted, yet he cheweth not the cud; he is unclean to you.","year":-1490},{"id":"recOXsvi6ZQ7k2CAR","ref":"Lev.11.8","text":"Of their flesh shall ye not eat, and their carcase shall ye not touch; they are unclean to you.","year":-1490}]}
